# Akan Name Generator

This is a simple web-based **Akan Name Generator**. Users can input their **day, month, and year of birth**, select their **gender**, and the app will calculate their **Akan name** based on the day of the week they were born.

## History of Akan Names

The Akan people of Ghana and Ivory Coast have a tradition of naming children according to the **day of the week they were born**. Each day has a male and female name. For example, a boy born on Friday is called **Kofi**, while a girl born on Sunday is called **Akosua**. These names are believed to influence personality and destiny, and they remain a symbol of cultural heritage and pride.

## Day Names Table

