|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| Sunday    | Kwasi     | Akosua      |
| Monday    | Kwadwo    | Adwoa       |
| Tuesday   | Kwabena   | Abenaa      |
| Wednesday | Kwaku     | Akua        |
| Thursday  | Yaw       | Yaa         |
| Friday    | Kofi      | Afua        |
| Saturday  | Kwame     | Ama         |

## How to Use

1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Enter your **day, month, and year of birth**.
3. Select your **gender**.
4. Click **Generate Akan Name** to see your name and the day of the week you were born.

